      "raw_text": "Mother Goose Up to Date\" will\nbe presented at the Spokane Fri\nday and Saturday evenings with a\nspecial matinee Saturday. The\nproduction is put on under the\nauspices of the Woman's club OF\nthis city and the proceeds will be\ndevoted to the new clubhouse. A\ncast of $50 people will appear I'M\nder direction of Halriet Purdy\nSmith. Bright lines and catchy\nmusic are promised in the modern\nMother Goose."
    }
